      "role": "user",
      "content": "i was looking at some old satellite maps of dc last night and i think i found something weird. the way the major avenues and the circles are laid out... it's not just random planning. when you trace the main lines, it looks like a specific geometric pattern, almost like a sigil or a seal. have u ever seen anything like that in the city layout?",
